query:
SELECT id, inspectionId, nozzleNumber, description, size, actualThickness, minRequiredThickness 
FROM nozzles 
WHERE inspectionId = (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTag = '57-11-001')
ORDER BY nozzleNumber;
